What's new in v1.4

Current Plan:
• Shows live price and next billing date
• Cancelled subscription warning with option to renew
• Warning when conflicting subscriptions are detected
• Lifetime upgrade option available from monthly/annual plan

Paywall:
• Shows "Then X/year from year 2" for first-year intro offers
• Prompts to cancel old subscription after upgrading to Lifetime

Spam Reporting:
• TRAI reporting option hidden for non-India devices

Your Plan:
• Plan status refreshes automatically when returning from Google Play
• Pending payment notice for UPI/cash purchases awaiting confirmation
• Scheduled plan change notice for deferred downgrades
• "View Purchase" now opens order history for Lifetime plan
• Redeem Google Play code now opens Play Store app directly
